---
title: Super Quick Satay Beef Rice Bowl with Green Beans and Salted Peanuts
description: Also spelled as 'sate' in Indonesia, satay typically consists of skewered meat served with peanut sauce. We're keeping it simple by simmering pork in peanut sauce that's ready in less than 15 minutes.
